 |work=Hall of Fame
 |title=Evan Shute & Wilfrid Shute
 |publisher=Orthomolecular.org
 |accessdate=2009-03-13
}}</ref> Several concepts now cited by orthomolecularists, including individual biochemical variation<ref name="autogenerated1" /> and [[Inborn error of metabolism|inborn errors of metabolism]],<ref name="Menolascino">
